{"tid":1221794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同撐中既屋企人真係溝通唔撚到","createTime":"2019-06-14T09:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:04:14.000Z","uid":56749,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cbee5300a41669b71791e3534d2edea6a22fe1da","tid":1221794,"uid":56749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"真係好撚嬲 平時睇連登都感受到好慘<br />\n已經無主動同佢地傾 一定嘈交<br />\n點知今日聽到佢地係咁講撐警察 無警察社會就好亂<br />\n入院既就係議員bla bla bla <br />\n仲話我盲撐 讀咁多書都無啲獨立思考<br />\n仲話中槍啲人收晒人錢 好撚辛苦 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為得啲廢老信 點知三十幾歲既兄弟姊妹都會信<br />\n收晒人錢咪又係啲人9up係到傳 信咗咪又係無獨立思考 唉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb35e3503a7c7640c6c34af995ca7e2dcd12b2a8","tid":1221794,"uid":56749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7909dbd80d690a0ba813cf320734ea73abed7fad","tid":1221794,"uid":38358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:04:14.000Z","msg":"加油"}]}